{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/getuserid"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)getUserId","symbolKind":"method","title":"getUserId","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"getUserId","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"getUserId","kind":"identifier"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Retrieves the current user identifier."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/getUserId","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSString","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"getUserId","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"return-value","text":"Return Value","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The current user identifier (custom user ID or HWID)"}]}],"kind":"content"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Returns the user ID that was previously set via ","type":"text"},{"code":"setUserId:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", or the HWID if no custom"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"user ID has been set."}]},{"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Sync user ID with analytics platforms:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class AnalyticsCoordinator {","","    func syncIdentifiers() {","        let userId = Pushwoosh.configure.getUserId()","        let hwid = Pushwoosh.configure.getHWID()","","        \/\/ Sync with various analytics platforms","        Analytics.identify(userId)","        Crashlytics.setUserID(userId)","        MixpanelInstance.identify(distinctId: userId)","","        \/\/ Log device mapping for debugging","        Logger.debug(\"User identity: userId=\\(userId), hwid=\\(hwid)\")","    }","","    func trackEventWithUserContext(_ event: String, properties: [String: Any]) {","        var enrichedProperties = properties","        enrichedProperties[\"pushwoosh_user_id\"] = Pushwoosh.configure.getUserId()","        enrichedProperties[\"pushwoosh_hwid\"] = Pushwoosh.configure.getHWID()","","        Analytics.track(event, properties: enrichedProperties)","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}],"title":"PushwooshCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/getUserId":{"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"getUserId","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/getUserId","url":"\/documentati